  skillName: "Nhai S\xE0i"
  skillDescription: "Sau khi b\u1EA1n nh\u1EADn s\xE1t th\u01B0\u01A1ng, b\u1EA1n
    c\xF3 th\u1EC3 l\u1EC7nh ngu\u1ED3n s\xE1t th\u01B0\u01A1ng l\u1EF1a ch\u1ECDn
    m\u1ED9t h\u1EA1ng m\u1EE5c:\r\n\r\nB\u1ECF \u0111i m\u1ED9t n\u1EEDa l\u01B0\u1EE3ng
    b\xE0i tr\xEAn tay (l\xE0m tr\xF2n l\xEAn).\r\nH\u1ECD kh\xF4ng th\u1EC3 ti\u1EBFp
    t\u1EE5c s\u1EED d\u1EE5ng b\xE0i tr\xEAn tay l\u01B0\u1EE3t hi\u1EC7n t\u1EA1i,
    sau \u0111\xF3 b\u1EA1n r\xFAt hai l\xE1 b\xE0i.\r\nM\u1EDF ra t\u1EA5t c\u1EA3
    b\xE0i tr\xEAn tay c\u1EE7a h\u1ECD, sau \u0111\xF3 giao cho b\u1EA1n t\u1EA5t
    c\u1EA3 b\xE0i m\u1ED9t lo\u1EA1i ch\u1EA5t trong b\xE0i tr\xEAn tay.\r\n\xBBThanh
    \u0110\xE0m\xAB"
  urlVoice: []
